The '''chromosphere''' was a layer of [[Atmosphere/Legends|atmosphere]] of a [[Star/Legends|star]]. It laid between the [[Photosphere/Legends|photosphere]] and the [[Corona (layer)|corona]]. [[Magnetic loop]]s sometimes occurred in the chromosphere and [[Solar flare/Legends|stellar flares]] were formed here. In [[3986 BBY]], [[Vima Sunrider]] hijacked an ion [[Mining/Legends|mining]] [[Starship/Legends|ship]] from [[Exis Station/Legends|Exis Station]] and flew it perilously close to the chromosphere of a nearby star.

